  "description": "Kitchen-sink stake-pool query pinned to one pool. Many subqueries drift (activeStake per epoch, blocks as they're produced, delegators join/leave, rewards per epoch, retirements, metadataHash on updates), so we mask aggressively and assert on the stable pool-identity fields (hash, id, margin, pledge, owners, rewardAddress).",
  "expected": {
